    "title": "How can I convert byte size into a human-readable format in Java?",
    "body": "<p>How can I convert byte size into a human-readable format in Java?</p>\n<p>Like 1024 should become &quot;1 Kb&quot; and 1024*1024 should become &quot;1 Mb&quot;.</p>\n<p>I am kind of sick of writing this utility method for each project. Is there a static method in <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Apache Commons</a> for this?</p>\n"
  },
